729924f-b.text:
(1)
Wiman Place (left, not seen), east side, noeth of Clifton Ave. Tnis house belonged to C.O'Connor (1874 map), Brennan (1898 to 1907 maps), and later (1917 map) to Emily McAndrews. The
view is northward from Clifton Ave.
Fcbruary 25, 1931.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
A view of the east side of the house as viewed westward along
Sylva Lane from near Edgewater Street.
February 25, 1931.
P. L. Sperr.
(3)
A distant view of the house in a northwesterly direction.
February 25, 1931.
P. S. Sperr.
